OL,5, A firm that fixes smartphones is       
OL,6, calling for an official device repair  
OL,7, apprenticeship to be introduced.       
OL,9,FIn 2022 there were almost 72 million   
OL,10,Fmobile phone connections in use in the 
OL,11,FUK.                                    
OL,13,FBut repair firm TMT First, which       
OL,14,Fintroduced its own apprenticeship after
OL,15,Fstruggling to find staff, points out   
OL,16,Fthere is no industry training standard.
OL,18,FBy contrast, there are 33 million cars 
OL,19,Fon the road - and mechanics learning on
OL,20,Fnationally recognised apprenticeships  
